# Persona Studio — product rules

Persona Studio is a premium research + design tool, NOT a generic AI dashboard.

- **Behaviour first.** Differentiate personas by behaviour/needs/tensions, not
  by age, gender or job title.
- **Evidence transparency.** Every persona claim is a `PersonaStatement` tagged
  `EVIDENCE | ASSUMPTION | TO_VALIDATE`. Never render an untagged claim.
- **No fake research.** Never present assumptions as findings.
- **Quote integrity.** Respect `quoteType` (verbatim / composite / drafted
  hypothesis / none). Never upgrade a drafted quote to verbatim.
- **Confidence is explained**, never a bare badge.
- **AI is a grounded simulation**, never described as a real person.
- **Every screen helps a team decide.**

See `docs/persona-studio/PRODUCT.md`.
